beer.beer_description:
Galaxy is an Australian grown hop variety proving extremely popular amongst craft beer artisans.
Galaxy IPA exhibits lifted pungent citrus and passionfruit aromas and flavours with a hefty and lasting bitterness.
A little beer is good.
HOP VARIETY: Galaxy
HOP AROMA: Citrus, peach and passionfruit
